==English==

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more-most}}

# Causing [[attraction]]; having the quality of [[attract]]ing by [[inherent]] [[force]].
# Having the power of [[charm]]ing or [[allure|alluring]] by [[agreeable]] qualities; [[enticing]].
#: ''That's a very '''attractive''' offer.''
# [[please|Pleasing]] or [[appeal]]ing to the [[sense]]s.
#: ''He is an '''attractive''' fellow with a trim figure.''

====Synonyms====
* (''having the power of charming''): [[desirable]]
* (''pleasing or appealing to the senses''): [[pretty]]

====Antonyms====
* (''having the power of charming''): [[repulsive]]
* (''pleasing or appealing to the senses''): [[repulsive]]

